videos.headline: Wisconsin TE hauls in first TD of year
videos.description: Wisconsin QB Alex Hornibrook finds TE Eric Steffes in the end zone to give the Badgers a 7-3 lead over Michigan State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wisconsin TE hauls in first TD of year) 2016/09/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wisconsin returns Michigan State fumble 66 yards for TD
videos.description: Michigan State RB LJ Scott fumbles and Leo Musso picks it up and returns it 66 yards to give Wisconsin a 20-6 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wisconsin returns Michigan State fumble 66 yards for TD) 2016/09/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wisconsin takes commanding 30-6 lead over Michigan State
videos.description: Wisconsin takes advantage of a botched Michigan State punt with Corey Clement scoring from five yards out on the next play to put the Badgers ahead 30-6.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wisconsin takes commanding 30-6 lead over Michigan State) 2016/09/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: T.J. Watt gets the sack for the Badgers
videos.description: J.J. Watt's brother T.J. sacks Michigan State QB Tyler O'Connor in the fourth quarter for Wisconsin.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (T.J. Watt gets the sack for the Badgers) 2016/09/24 ESHEET
